graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller Manager]
        Controller -->|reconciles| DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
        Controller -->|deploys| Components[DSP Components]
    end

    subgraph "DSP Stack (per namespace)"
        direction TB

        subgraph "API & Control Plane"
            APIServer[DS Pipelines API Server<br/>KFP v1/v2 REST/gRPC API]
            PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Workflow State Sync]
            ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>CronJob Management]
        end

        subgraph "Workflow Execution"
            WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>Argo Workflows 3.x<br/>namespace-scoped]
        end

        subgraph "ML Metadata"
            MLMDServer[MLMD gRPC Server<br/>ML lineage tracking]
            MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>OAuth-protected access]
        end

        subgraph "Storage"
            MariaDB[(MariaDB<br/>Pipeline metadata & runs)]
            Minio[(Minio<br/>Artifacts & logs)]
        end

        APIServer -->|orchestrates| WorkflowController
        PersistenceAgent -->|syncs state| APIServer
        ScheduledWF -->|triggers| APIServer
        APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
        APIServer -->|accesses| MLMDEnvoy
        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies to| MLMDServer
        MLMDServer -->|stores| MariaDB
        WorkflowController -->|stores artifacts| Minio
        WorkflowController -->|creates| PipelinePods[Pipeline Pods]
        PipelinePods -->|reads/writes| Minio
        PipelinePods -->|reports to| APIServer
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR
    User -->|submits pipelines| Route[OpenShift Route<br/>OAuth2 Protected]
    Route -->|forwards to| APIServer

    Workbench[Workbenches/Notebooks<br/>KFP SDK] -->|submits| Route
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|integrates| Route

    Components -.->|deploys| APIServer
    Components -.->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Components -.->|deploys| ScheduledWF
    Components -.->|deploys| WorkflowController
    Components -.->|deploys| MLMDServer
    Components -.->|deploys| MLMDEnvoy
    Components -.->|deploys| MariaDB
    Components -.->|deploys| Minio

    WorkflowController -->|uses| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Pod orchestration]
    Controller -->|uses| K8sAPI

    ExternalS3[External S3<br/>AWS/GCS/Azure] -.->|alternative to| Minio
    ExternalDB[External Database<br/>RDS/CloudSQL] -.->|alternative to| MariaDB

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623
    style APIServer fill:#7ed321
    style WorkflowController fill:#7ed321
    style MariaDB fill:#bd10e0
    style Minio fill:#bd10e0
    style Route fill:#f5a623
    style K8sAPI fill:#999
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8
